shibboleth.actions

Class GetAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • shibboleth.actions.ShibbolethAction
      • shibboleth.actions.GetAction

  • public class GetAction
extends ShibbolethAction
    Retrieve a Github artifact, i.e. a user, repo or contributions. Subsequently store it to the database and add to the graph. Syntax: get [repo|user] -- Retrieve and add to graph get -c [repo|user|-all] (-l) -- Retrieve contributions available locally, -l = all languages get -ca [repo|user] (-l) -- Retrieve all contributions get -cu [repo] -- Retrieve all full user descriptions (Github API intensive).
    Author:
    Wilco Wisse
